abstract: "Derived, de-identified analytic label tables, figure source data, statistical outputs, table source files and custom scripts supporting the manuscript Informal learning in everyday human-LLM interaction. The release intentionally excludes raw message text, original conversation identifiers, URLs, timestamps, user identifiers, linked user histories and API keys."
